data.description: Attractive 2020 Saratoga Homes home is now available in the beautiful Kingdom Heights family-based community. Enjoy and relax in the efficient and spacious 2 story, 3 Bedroom, 3 full Bath home with Dining, open Kitchen and Living floor plan, Study, Utility Room, large upstairs Game Room and 2-car Garage. Spacious Primary Bedroom Suite can accommodate a King size bed and features large walk-in closet. Primary Bathroom includes separate tub, walk-in shower and separate sinks. Substantial size Kitchen includes granite counter tops, island and breakfast area, perfect for both families and entertaining. Beautiful flooring and newly installed carpet downstairs and stairwell. High ceilings, recessed lighting, newly painted walls and front yard landscaping. Enjoy outdoor fun and cooking in large back yard! Located adjacent to Recreation & Event Center, exercise facility and swimming pool. This “move-in ready” home is a must see. Schedule your showing today!
